Singham Core

Core moderation and management framework for FriendsMP.

Built for modern Minecraft communities with a clean punishment system, reputation tracking, staff utilities, and database syncing.

Overview

Singham Core is a lightweight but scalable Paper plugin focused on moderation, player management, and staff tooling.

The project is designed around:

performance
clean architecture
async database operations
modern moderation workflows
future web integration
